name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc: Version 20
overview: Playable demos: Paper Mario: The Thousand-Year Door, Mario Power Tennis, Metroid Prime 2: Echoes, Resident Evil 4, Viewtiful Joe 2, Baten Kaitos: Eternal Wings and the Lost Ocean, and Mario Party 6. The disc also features pre-release trailers of the following: Metroid Prime 2: Echoes, Geist, Resident Evil 4, Tony Hawk's Underground 2, GoldenEye: Rogue Agent, X-Men Legends, Need for Speed: Underground 2, Mario Party 6, and the Nintendo DS.
